Package org.spongepowered.api.world.generation.config.noise

Interface NoiseRouter

public interface NoiseRouter
Noise Router for world generation. See NoiseGeneratorConfigs NoiseGeneratorConfig.noiseRouter() for the default routers used by vanilla.
